.SH NAME
t4_get_port_stats \- collect port statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" t4_get_port_stats
.BI "(struct adapter *adap "  ","
.BI "int idx "  ","
.BI "struct port_stats *p "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "adap" 12
the adapter
.IP "idx" 12
the port index
.IP "p" 12
the stats structure to fill

Collect statistics related to the given port from HW.
